- if activity.recipient.is_owned_by?(@current_user)
  | ¡Enhorabuena! Tu plan en el restaurante #{activity.trackable.restaurant.name} el día #{activity.trackable.date}
- else
  | Tonight's plan dinner for 
  == cell(:user, activity.recipient).show_link
  |  at restaurant
  == cell(:restaurant, activity.trackable.restaurant).show_link